ets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.bumjhf97uy7d-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.bumjhf97uy7d-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.bumjhf97uy7d-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.bumjhf97uy7d-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.bumjhf97uy7d-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a><br /> （来自<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q5DLvjXmnFM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">吉永鲁奈的分配槽</a>）</p><p>第二节的谜题是<strong>“三线索金字塔”，</strong>您必须猜测与三个线索相关的单词。第一个回答40个问题的女孩将被清除，但回答的是观众。这种责任压在你身上。</p><p>女孩们像主播一样实时与观众互动，加深互动。不过，本作的一个特点是，当观众输掉比赛时，越执着，对观众的伤害就会越大。顺便说一句，<strong>这场比赛的受害者是同时观看人数最高的“风张美里”。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.7mp3111r3dy-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.7mp3111r3dy-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.7mp3111r3dy-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.7mp3111r3dy-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1b90833bd6acdc29e21990cf5f1-kix.7mp3111r3dy-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a><br /> （摘自<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0EAslE-QnDw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">风张美里的配线架</a>）</p><p>被淘汰的人被设定了忏悔时间，风张美里承认了自己所藏的弥天大谎。直接处决的场景没有展示，但在风张美里的镜头下，观众们无言以对，说“很难”“住手”，为无法保护自己而道歉，说“对不起”，并愤怒于游戏大师收到了这样的评论。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/cbffe1